had-cky@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cky">CKY</a>主唱查德·金斯伯格 (Chad I Ginsburg) 声称，出于自卫，他打了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alien-ant-farm">外星蚂蚁农场 (Alien Ant Farm)</a>的德莱顿·米切尔 (Dryden Mitchell) 的脸 - 看看金斯伯格在下面怎么说。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/primal-scream-bobby-gillespie-interview-come-ahead-3810374">原始尖叫在他们的抗议迪斯科专辑中：“如果你要从屋顶尖叫，没有比这更好的时机了”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末（11 月 9 日），Alien Ant Farm 和 CKY 拉开了联合巡演英国站的序幕， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farm-cky-joint-uk-tour-with-1-ticket-levy-for-grassroots-venues-buy-tickets-3752024">该巡演早在 4 月份就已宣布</a>。然而，就在马盖特梦幻世界开幕前几个小时，外星人蚂蚁农场的德莱顿·米切尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farms-dryden-mitchell-kicks-cky-off-tour-after-frontman-chad-i-ginsburg-punches-him-in-the-face-3811273">宣布 CKY 被取消巡演</a>。</p><p>当时，米切尔解释说，他曾质问金斯伯格，称他“在欧洲演出中对待多名工作人员和开场乐队成员就像垃圾一样，并在我们的营地引起了普遍的戏剧性事件”，然后他被打了一拳。 </p><figure id="attachment_3811438" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811438" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811438" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811438" class="wp-caption-